.TH CLOCK UCB 2/24/79 UCB
.SH NAME
clock \- continually print the time of the day
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B clock
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Clock
continually prints the time of day.
.PP
A quit signal stops the clock; another quit restarts it.
.SH BUGS
.I Clock
must be run on a \s-2CRT\s0.
.PP
.I Clock
is monotonous.
